#                 _tailon             [Go=231 CONTINUED Axis 176, slot 2/0/0]
#
#     JS/Node : @iarna/toml           by Rebecca Turner (iarna/zkat at
#                                      npm); spec-complete TOML 1.0
#                                      parser + serializer.  Powers
#                                      npm-cli itself (which Rebecca
#                                      authored at the time), Vercel
#                                      `.env`/TOML tooling, Rollup +
#                                      esbuild config layers, and most
#                                      Node tools that read TOML.
#                                      Pairs in the modern Node ecosystem
#                                      with `@ltd/j-toml` (LongTengDao)
#                                      + `smol-toml` (cyyynthia, used by
#                                      Prettier + Vercel + Astro).
#                 → cannon (@usecannon/cli — usecannon collective's EVM
#                           deployment orchestrator; Cannonfile.toml
#                           describes named ops [deploy.MyToken] /
#                           [contract.Counter] / [invoke.Token.transfer]
#                           composing into reproducible IPFS-addressed
#                           on-chain deployments; 124★ GPL-3.0)
#                 _cannon            [TS-Node=231 CLOSES Axis 176, 1/1/1]
#                                                  ↑↑↑ THIS FILE ↑↑↑
#                 @iarna/toml is the de-facto npm TOML parser by virtue
